TITLE: Nullish Coalescing - Good Example TSX
DESCRIPTION: Shows the preferred way of using the nullish-coalescing operator `??` to only return the default value when the value is strictly `null` or `undefined`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/twentyhq/twenty/blob/main/packages/twenty-website/src/content/developers/frontend-development/style-guide.mdx#_snippet_9

