TITLE: Start Cron Jobs (Google/Microsoft)
DESCRIPTION: Registers recurring jobs for messaging and calendar synchronization using yarn commands. These commands are executed from the worker container and handle importing messages, fetching message lists, fetching calendar event lists, importing calendar events, and managing stale data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/twentyhq/twenty/blob/main/packages/twenty-website/src/content/developers/self-hosting/setup.mdx#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
# from your worker container
yarn command:prod cron:messaging:messages-import
yarn command:prod cron:messaging:message-list-fetch
yarn command:prod cron:calendar:calendar-event-list-fetch
yarn command:prod cron:calendar:calendar-events-import
yarn command:prod cron:messaging:ongoing-stale
yarn command:prod cron:calendar:ongoing-stale
```

