TITLE: Radio Button Usage with Twenty UI
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the Radio component from the twenty-ui library.  It initializes a Radio component with props like checked, value, onChange, onCheckedChange, size, disabled, and labelPosition.  onChange logs the event target's checked state, while onCheckedChange logs the checked boolean value.
